    </P>

    <Label color={C.amber}>The Session Boundary Problem</Label>
    <Note color={C.amber} glow={C.amberGlow} icon="⚡">
      <B>The core tension:</B> Claude Code doesn't have native "session" boundaries. It's a persistent
